tip.text: Great menu with a large selection of different dishes, including steaks, burgers and salads. Good service. Had the rib eye for lunch. Was excellent.
Located inside the Forrest and close to the water, you can enjoy a lunch or dinner while listening to birds and enjoying a gentle breeze from the beach. Very affordable. Great service. Local produce.
